        <time datetime="2020-04-12T16:47:00-04:00" class="tnt-date asset-date text-muted">Apr 12, 2020</time></li><li class="card-comment-count"><a href="/news/local/covid-19-disrupts-virginia-tourism-ahead-of-peak-season/article_c407ecd1-e046-54d1-835e-7b166a169fc2.html#comments" class="cm" title="0 comments"><span class="fas tnt-comments"></span> <span class="count">0</span></a></li></ul>
