            Charlottesville area African Americans hospitalized for virus at higher rates</a></h3></div><div class="card-meta">
            <ul class="list-inline">
                        <li class="card-byline text-muted"><span id="author-528b4a36-e6a8-11e8-b097-3b862e4549c5-asset-caebbf93-bf9b-506c-8676-2f09115e79ed" class="tnt-byline asset-byline"  >By KATHERINE KNOTT
