                            <div class="card-lead">
                                <p class="tnt-summary"><p>The data mirrors an emerging national trend and is an example of how, in the four weeks since the first case was reported in Charlottesville, the health district is still struggling to overcome testing obstacles to get a sense of the virus' spread throughout existing fault lines.</p></p>
