        </div><div class="card-headline"><h3 class="tnt-headline ">
        
             <a href="/news/local/trump-winery-eligible-for-bailout-in-virus-relief-law/article_c81a4662-622b-53db-abab-e43399da1134.html" class="tnt-asset-link">
        

        
            Trump Winery eligible for bailout in virus relief law</a></h3></div><div class="card-meta">
            <ul class="list-inline">
                        <li class="card-byline text-muted"><span  class="tnt-byline">The Associated Press

</span></li><li class="card-date">
        <time datetime="2020-04-10T18:37:00-04:00" class="tnt-date asset-date text-muted">Apr 10, 2020</time></li><li class="card-comment-count"><a href="/news/local/trump-winery-eligible-for-bailout-in-virus-relief-law/article_c81a4662-622b-53db-abab-e43399da1134.html#comments" class="cm" title="3 comments"><span class="fas tnt-comments"></span> <span class="count">3</span></a></li></ul>
        </div>
                    
                    
                    
                    
                        
                        
                            <div class="card-lead">
                                <p class="tnt-summary"><p>Deep in the fine print of the law passed by Congress to try to arrest an economic free fall is language that would the make the vineyard eligible for aid extended to growers and producers of “specialty crops,” among them grapes used to make wine.</p></p>
                            </div>
                        
                    
                    
                    
                    
                    
