        </div><div class="card-headline"><h3 class="tnt-headline ">
        
             <a href="/news/local/charlottesville-attorney-files-suit-seeking-release-of-certain-prisoners-amid-covid-19-pandemic/article_ba5098b0-5b14-5e73-ba57-a7b59285e84a.html" class="tnt-asset-link">
        

        
            Charlottesville attorney files suit seeking release of certain prisoners amid COVID-19 pandemic</a></h3></div><div class="card-meta">
            <ul class="list-inline">
                        <li class="card-byline text-muted"><span id="author-409fd64e-f003-11e7-a5ae-3b6be71044b5-asset-ba5098b0-5b14-5e73-ba57-a7b59285e84a" class="tnt-byline asset-byline"  >By TYLER HAMMEL
thammel@dailyprogress.com | (434) 978-7268 </span>
                </li><li class="card-date">
        <time datetime="2020-04-09T12:47:00-04:00" class="tnt-date asset-date text-muted">Apr 9, 2020</time></li><li class="card-comment-count"><a href="/news/local/charlottesville-attorney-files-suit-seeking-release-of-certain-prisoners-amid-covid-19-pandemic/article_ba5098b0-5b14-5e73-ba57-a7b59285e84a.html#comments" class="cm" title="3 comments"><span class="fas tnt-comments"></span> <span class="count">3</span></a></li></ul>
        </div>
                    
                    
                    
                    
                        
                        
                            <div class="card-lead">
                                <p class="tnt-summary"><p>The 47-page suit asks the federal court to declare that the defendants’ failure to enact policies to reduce population density at prisons amid a pandemic creates an imminent risk to the plaintiffs’ health that violates their Eighth Amendment right to be free of cruel and unusual punishment.</p></p>
                            </div>
                        
                    
                    
                    
                    
                    
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="clearfix"></div>
        </article>
                    
                </div>
            
                <div class="collection-card">
                    
                        <article id="card-summary-8a0f442d-e9a2-53d3-a19d-afdd01b7313f" class="clearfix card summary   tnt-section-news tnt-sub-section-state">
            <div class="card-container">
                
                <div class="card-body"><div class="card-labels">
            
                <div class="card-label-section text-muted">
                    <a href="/news/state/" class="tnt-section-tag">State</a>
                </div>
            
            
                <div class="card-label-flags">
                    <span class="tnt-flag label label-flag label-flag-default label-flag-top-story">top story</span> 
                </div>
            
        </div><div class="card-headline"><h3 class="tnt-headline ">
        
             <a href="/news/state/aclu-others-call-for-urgent-prison-and-jail-releases-in-response-to-covid-19/article_8a0f442d-e9a2-53d3-a19d-afdd01b7313f.html" class="tnt-asset-link">
        

        
            ACLU, others call for urgent prison and jail releases in response to COVID-19</a></h3></div><div class="card-meta">
            <ul class="list-inline">
                        <li class="card-byline text-muted"><span  class="tnt-byline">BY FRANK GREEN
Richmond Times-Dispatch</span></li><li class="card-date">
        <time datetime="2020-04-09T10:10:00-04:00" class="tnt-date asset-date text-muted">Apr 9, 2020</time></li><li class="card-comment-count"><a href="/news/state/aclu-others-call-for-urgent-prison-and-jail-releases-in-response-to-covid-19/article_8a0f442d-e9a2-53d3-a19d-afdd01b7313f.html#comments" class="cm" title="0 comments"><span class="fas tnt-comments"></span> <span class="count">0</span></a></li></ul>
        </div>
                    
                    
                    
                    
                        
                        
                            <div class="card-lead">
                                <p class="tnt-summary"><p>The ACLU of Virginia is calling for the quick release of any jail or prison inmate who does not pose "a demonstrable, imminent threat of bodily harm to others," in light of the threat posed behind bars by COVID-19.</p></p>
                            </div>
                        
                    
                    
                    
                    
                    
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="clearfix"></div>
        </article>
                    
                </div>
            
