            <ul class="list-inline">
                        <li class="card-byline text-muted"><span  class="tnt-byline">Richmond Times-Dispatch </span></li><li class="card-date">
        <time datetime="2020-03-28T14:11:00-04:00" class="tnt-date asset-date text-muted">Mar 28, 2020</time></li><li class="card-comment-count"><a href="/news/local/update-739-cases-of-coronavirus-in-virginia-and-17-deaths-tjhd-reports-42-cases/article_dcd5e8e9-6130-5edf-b8ac-d8b4e6358685.html#comments" class="cm" title="0 comments"><span class="fas tnt-comments"></span> <span class="count">0</span></a></li></ul>
        </div>
                    
                    
                    
                    
                        
                        
                            <div class="card-lead">
                                <p class="tnt-summary"><p>The VDH also said that 9,166 people have been tested for the virus, 99 have been hospitalized, and there have been 17 deaths.</p></p>
                            </div>
                        
                    
                    
                    
                    
                    
