                                <p class="tnt-summary">In less than two months, the novel coronavirus has gone from a distant worry for Virginians to a full-blown crisis.  </p>
                            </div>
                        
                    
                    
                    
                    
                    
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="clearfix"></div>
        </article>
                    
