                        <li class="card-byline text-muted"><span id="author-528b4a36-e6a8-11e8-b097-3b862e4549c5-asset-3def73f9-0bde-5eb0-a062-3ab4ffc2e027" class="tnt-byline asset-byline"  >By KATHERINE KNOTT
