        </div><div class="card-headline"><h3 class="tnt-headline ">
        
             <a href="/news/state/statewide-updates-va-health-officials-to-issue-new-guidance-for-testing-nursing-home-residents-114/article_30493068-16eb-5a6e-aab7-c49ad0f696e8.html" class="tnt-asset-link">
        

        
            STATEWIDE UPDATES: Va. health officials to issue new guidance for testing nursing home residents; 114 confirmed cases of COVID-19 in Va.</a></h3></div><div class="card-meta">
            <ul class="list-inline">
                        <li class="card-byline text-muted"><span  class="tnt-byline">Times-Dispatch Staff Reports</span></li><li class="card-date">
        <time datetime="2020-03-20T11:17:00-04:00" class="tnt-date asset-date text-muted">Mar 20, 2020</time></li><li class="card-comment-count"><a href="/news/state/statewide-updates-va-health-officials-to-issue-new-guidance-for-testing-nursing-home-residents-114/article_30493068-16eb-5a6e-aab7-c49ad0f696e8.html#comments" class="cm" title="0 comments"><span class="fas tnt-comments"></span> <span class="count">0</span></a></li></ul>
        </div>
                    
                    
                    
                    
                        
                        
