             <a href="/news/local/virginia-hospitals-could-be-overwhelmed-by-covid-19-state-wont-say-how-many-ventilators-it/article_e77bcd31-9c16-501d-8e42-51b83152277a.html" class="tnt-asset-link">
        

        
            Virginia hospitals could be overwhelmed by COVID-19, state won't say how many ventilators it has</a></h3></div><div class="card-meta">
            <ul class="list-inline">
                        <li class="card-byline text-muted"><span  class="tnt-byline">By BRIDGET BALCH
Richmond Times-Dispatch </span></li><li class="card-date">
        <time datetime="2020-03-17T20:30:00-04:00" class="tnt-date asset-date text-muted">Mar 17, 2020</time></li><li class="card-comment-count"><a href="/news/local/virginia-hospitals-could-be-overwhelmed-by-covid-19-state-wont-say-how-many-ventilators-it/article_e77bcd31-9c16-501d-8e42-51b83152277a.html#comments" class="cm" title="0 comments"><span class="fas tnt-comments"></span> <span class="count">0</span></a></li></ul>
        </div>
                    
                    
                    
                    
                        
                        
