            Virus' impact on local business: While retail could take a hit, others turn to telecommuting</a></h3></div><div class="card-meta">
            <ul class="list-inline">
                        <li class="card-byline text-muted"><span id="author-7fbcf3cc-4031-11e5-9aa4-b736e63cc9bb-asset-43cdfacb-40c3-5021-a95e-25b6d89d58ef" class="tnt-byline asset-byline"  >By ALLISON WRABEL
