                </li><li class="card-date">
        <time datetime="2020-03-14T19:29:00-04:00" class="tnt-date asset-date text-muted">Mar 14, 2020</time></li><li class="card-comment-count"><a href="/business/virus-impact-on-local-business-while-retail-could-take-a-hit-others-turn-to-telecommuting/article_43cdfacb-40c3-5021-a95e-25b6d89d58ef.html#comments" class="cm" title="0 comments"><span class="fas tnt-comments"></span> <span class="count">0</span></a></li></ul>
