        </div><div class="card-headline"><h3 class="tnt-headline ">
        
             <a href="/sports/how-four-virginia-head-coaches-dealt-with-the-ncaa-s-cancellations-of-championships/article_08a203b1-d726-573e-86f5-32309314f4a2.html" class="tnt-asset-link">
        

        
            How four Virginia head coaches dealt with the NCAA’s cancellations of championships</a></h3></div><div class="card-meta">
            <ul class="list-inline">
                        <li class="card-byline text-muted"><span id="author-ecbd6136-d408-11e9-b52b-7f2977bf0ef8-asset-08a203b1-d726-573e-86f5-32309314f4a2" class="tnt-byline asset-byline"  >By BENNETT CONLIN
bconlin@dailyprogress.com (434) 978-7451 </span>
                </li><li class="card-date">
        <time datetime="2020-03-14T09:40:00-04:00" class="tnt-date asset-date text-muted">Mar 14, 2020</time></li><li class="card-comment-count"><a href="/sports/how-four-virginia-head-coaches-dealt-with-the-ncaa-s-cancellations-of-championships/article_08a203b1-d726-573e-86f5-32309314f4a2.html#comments" class="cm" title="0 comments"><span class="fas tnt-comments"></span> <span class="count">0</span></a></li><li class="card-time-to-read"><div class="time-to-read-wrapper">
               <span class="fas tnt-book"></span>
               <span class="read-time">6 min to read</span>
           </div></li></ul>
        </div>
                    
                    
                    
                    
                        
                        
                            <div class="card-lead">
                                <p class="tnt-summary">The NCAA canceled all winter and spring championships Thursday as a reaction to the spread of the coronavirus. </p>
