            Virginia Tech to offer housing, dining rebate with in-person classes canceled</a></h3></div><div class="card-meta">
            <ul class="list-inline">
                        <li class="card-byline text-muted"><span  class="tnt-byline">BY JUSTIN MATTINGLY
