        <time datetime="2020-03-13T13:35:00-04:00" class="tnt-date asset-date text-muted">Mar 13, 2020</time></li><li class="card-comment-count"><a href="/news/state/virginia-tech-to-offer-housing-dining-rebate-with-in-person-classes-canceled/article_1251280d-11dc-5d02-ba86-fadf829f70b9.html#comments" class="cm" title="0 comments"><span class="fas tnt-comments"></span> <span class="count">0</span></a></li></ul>
