        </div><div class="card-headline"><h3 class="tnt-headline ">
        
             <a href="/news/uva/uva-cancels-spring-break-study-abroad-programs/article_9e1c1667-8687-5cf5-9578-6766a9151494.html" class="tnt-asset-link">
        

        
            UVa cancels spring break study abroad programs</a></h3></div><div class="card-meta">
            <ul class="list-inline">
                        <li class="card-byline text-muted"><span id="author-610aa16a-298c-11e5-bd92-0b4bb9e85443-asset-9e1c1667-8687-5cf5-9578-6766a9151494" class="tnt-byline asset-byline"  >From staff reports </span>
                </li><li class="card-date">
        <time datetime="2020-03-04T10:20:00-05:00" class="tnt-date asset-date text-muted">Mar 4, 2020</time></li><li class="card-comment-count"><a href="/news/uva/uva-cancels-spring-break-study-abroad-programs/article_9e1c1667-8687-5cf5-9578-6766a9151494.html#comments" class="cm" title="0 comments"><span class="fas tnt-comments"></span> <span class="count">0</span></a></li></ul>
        </div>
                    
                    
                    
                    
                        
                        
                            <div class="card-lead">
                                <p class="tnt-summary"><p>Provost Liz Magill clarified that the decision came following recommendations from the Centers For Disease Control that universities should “reconsider” study abroad travel amid coronavirus concerns.</p></p>
                            </div>
                        
                    
                    
                    
                    
                    
                </div>
